Revision history for Rex-GPU

{{$NEXT}}
  - Initial release
  - GPU hardware detection via PCI class codes (NVIDIA, AMD)
  - NVIDIA driver installation (Debian/Ubuntu, RHEL/Rocky, openSUSE)
  - NVIDIA Container Toolkit installation
  - Containerd runtime configuration (RKE2, K3s, standalone)
  - Requires Rex::LibSSH (set connection => 'LibSSH') for SFTP-less hosts
  - Clear error when connecting to SFTP-less host without LibSSH backend
  - eg/Rexfile example for GPU detection and cluster deployment
